[[国际红十字会|国际红十字会]]说，加沙地带的医院已经无法处理更多的伤员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081229?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=10112 |title=Israel mounts third day of Gaza raids |accessdate=2009-01-04 |archive-date=2008-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081230123403/http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081229?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=10112 |dead-url=no }}</ref>红十字会发言人在加沙表示，当地医院需要更多的药品。据以色列国防军说，以色列允许一些土耳其捐赠救护车从西岸运往加沙地带，以及医疗用品给红十字会，近东救济工程处，[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]和[[无国界医生|无国界医生]]。<ref name="bamahane">{{cite news|url=http://dover.idf.il/IDF/News_Channels/today/08/12/2902.htm|title=Ambulances from West Bank Transported to Gaza Strip|publisher=[[Bamahane|Bamahane]]|author=Sneh, Rani|date=2008-12-29|accessdate=2008-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124163835/http://dover.idf.il/IDF/News_Channels/today/08/12/2902.htm|archive-date=2009-01-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同一天以色列南部城市[[亚实基伦|亚实基伦]]遭到火箭弹袭击，一名阿拉伯裔以色列建筑工人被炸死，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/three-israelis-killed-as-hamas-launches-revenge-attacks-1216226.html |title=Three Israelis killed as Hamas launches revenge attacks |accessdate=2009-01-04 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617062445/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/three-israelis-killed-as-hamas-launches-revenge-attacks-1216226.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外有3人受重伤。面对哈马斯持续不断的火箭弹袭击，迫于国内越来越大的压力，以色列政府在边界沿线集结步兵和装甲部队。<ref>{{Cite news
