=== 12月30日 ===
以军继续空袭加沙。伊斯兰大学、哈马斯训练中心、两处哈马斯训练营和[[人民抵抗委员会|人民抵抗委员会]]的办事处均遭到袭击；造成10人死亡。<ref>{{cite news |first=Nidal |last=al-Mughrabi |title=WRAPUP 1-Israel presses on with Gaza air attacks, 10 dead |url=http://africa.reuters.com/wire/news/usnLU691622.html |publisher=Reuters |date=2008-12-30 |accessdate=2008-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081231121426/http://africa.reuters.com/wire/news/usnLU691622.html |archive-date=2008-12-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>据[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]报道，以色列军方官员说，他们现在的目标不仅仅是哈马斯武装和其武器库，还包括了其“庞大”的支持网。<ref name="reuterstruce">[http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081230 Israel rejects truce, presses on with Gaza strikes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081230 |date=20201027175214 }} Reuters 2008-12-30</ref>

美联社报道说，一些加沙居民说，以色列最初的空袭没有任何警告，但以色列军队声称，他们空投警报传单和广播要求加沙居民离开住所，并且不要隐藏武器或武装分子。<ref>[http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5jwiDL_nGeC63bi_l8-3JB2WVc1xwD95CLD880 Israeli airstrikes kill dozens of Gaza civilians] [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] 2008-12-30</ref>[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]认为没有安全的地方为加沙平民提供庇护。<ref>[http://english.pnn.ps/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4369&Itemid=1 Amnesty International: there are no safe places in Gaza] {{Wayback|url=http://english.pnn.ps/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4369&Itemid=1 |date=20090121053913 }} [[Palestine_News_Network|Palestine News Network]] 2009-01-01</ref>

以色列关闭了一些距离边界大约30公里的学校，理由是担心更多的火箭弹袭击。当地居民被告知待在室内，提高对火箭弹来袭的警觉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081230?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=0 |title=Reuters Dec 30 |accessdate=2009-01-06 |archive-date=2008-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081231121828/http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSLS69391620081230?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以色列南部城市[[贝尔谢巴|贝尔谢巴]]一间无人的幼儿园遭到袭击，造成严重损坏。哈马斯从加沙向以色列境内发射了24枚卡萨姆火箭和11枚迫击炮弹造成一些破坏，但无人受伤。<ref name="dec31">[[CNN|CNN]] [http://www.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/12/21/israel.gaza/index.html#cnnSTCText?iref=werecommend Israel fires back at Gaza, as Israeli PM vows more] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/12/21/israel.gaza/index.html#cnnSTCText?iref=werecommend |date=20081224022019 }}, December 31, 2008</ref>

埃及表示如果巴勒斯坦民族权力机构能够控制边界过境点的话，埃及将会全面开放边界。<ref>[http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/pages/ShArtStEng.jhtml?itemNo=1051238&contrassID=1&subContrassID=1&title='Mubarak:%20We'll%20open%20Gaza%20crossing%20only%20if%20Abbas'%20PA%20takes%20control%20of%20it'&dyn_server=172.20.5.5 Mubarak: We'll open Gaza crossing only if PA takes control] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/pages/ShArtStEng.jhtml?itemNo=1051238&contrassID=1&subContrassID=1&title='Mubarak:%20We'll%20open%20Gaza%20crossing%20only%20if%20Abbas'%20PA%20takes%20control%20of%20it'&dyn_server=172.20.5.5 |date=20081231103334 }}, ''Haaretz'', 31-12-2008</ref>

以色列一直禁止记者进入加沙地带，理由是“安全”问题。一份提出的400个外国记者进入加沙地带的呈请书已经提交给以色列最高法院。<ref name="reportersdec30">{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/dec/30/israel-gaza-journalists |title=Foreign journalists demand Gaza access |accessdate=2009-01-06 |archive-date=2012-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114134516/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/dec/30/israel-gaza-journalists |dead-url=no }}</ref>

以色列表示将允许更多的援助的卡车进入加沙，并且已经有100辆运送人道主义物资的卡车通过[[凯雷姆沙洛姆|凯雷姆沙洛姆]]进入加沙地带。5辆[[土耳其|土耳其]]捐赠的新救护车也被允许进入加沙地带。众多国际援助卡车也已经为进入加沙地带。<ref>{{cite web |title = Israel lets 100 aid trucks into Gaza via Kerem Shalom border crossing |url = http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230456528631&pagename=JPost/JPArticle/ShowFull |publisher = [[Jerusalem_Post|Jerusalem Post]] |date = 2008-12-30 |language = en }}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/detaylar.do?load=detay&link=162783 Turkish aid to arrive in Gaza Strip on Thursday]{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

=== 12月31日 ===
当天有42名巴勒斯坦人死于以军的空袭。近东救济工程处报告说，在死亡者中至少有25%是平民。<ref>{{cite news|title=25 percent of Gaza killed civilians: UN|url=http://www.metimes.com/Politics/2008/12/31/25_percent_of_gaza_killed_civilians_un/afp/|date=2009-12-31}}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>以色列继续轰炸“几十个目标”，包括了由埃及进入加沙地带的走私通道。<ref name=HAA2>[http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1051542.html Israel decides to push on with Gaza op until 'all goals reached'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1051542.html |date=20091226145524 }} Haaretz, 31 December 2008</ref>

当天上午，两枚来自加沙地带火箭弹击中了以色列城市贝尔谢巴；其中一枚击中了一所学校，造成严重损毁，但没有人员伤亡，因为以色列政府的指示学校继续停课。两枚火箭落在以色列城市亚实基伦，造成两人轻伤；还有一些火箭弹落在其他的以色列城镇中。<ref name="dec31_ynetnews">[[ynetnews|ynetnews]] [http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3647765,00.html Rocket hits Beersheba school; no injuries] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3647765,00.html |date=20171101154312 }}, December 31, 2008</ref>总的来说，超过60枚卡秋莎和卡萨姆火箭弹袭击了以色列。<ref name = "Haaretz 1051235">{{cite news | url = http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1051235.html | title = 4 rockets hit south as 'special situation' status extended to 40 kilometers from Gaza border | publisher = Haaretz | location = Jerusalem, IL | accessdate = 2009-01-03 | date = 2008-12-31 | first = Yanir | last = Yagna | archive-date = 2010-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100327204609/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1051235.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="dec31a">[[CNN|CNN]] [https://web.archive.org/web/20090101180426/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090101/ap_on_re_mi_ea/ml_israel_palestinians Israel sends more troops to Gaza border], December 31, 2008</ref>

以色列拒绝法国外交部长[[贝尔纳·库什内|贝尔纳·库什内]]提出48小时停火建议。<ref name="bbc_dec_31_truce">{{cite news |title=Israel rejects Gaza truce calls |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7805558.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2008-12-31 |accessdate=2008-12-31 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5dU02mthA?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7805558.stm |archivedate=2008-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>与此同时，哈马斯发言人艾曼告诉法新社，哈马斯愿意接受任何停火建议，来结束以色列的空袭，并停止在加沙的封锁。在以色列内阁会议上，以色列安全局（Shin Bet）表示，哈马斯已经遭受了重大损失，许多哈马斯人员冒充医务人员躲藏在医院，或匿藏于清真寺里，把这些建筑当成总部。他们认为以色列不会攻击这些建筑。<ref name="ynet_hamas_gunmen_hiding_in_hospitals">{{cite web |title = Gaza: Hamas gunmen hide in hospitals |url = http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3648020,00.html |publisher = [[YNET|YNET]] |date = 2008-12-31 |language = en |accessdate = 2009-01-06 |archive-date = 2009-01-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090101103034/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0%2C7340%2CL-3648020%2C00.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 1月1日 ===
以军空袭了加沙的议会大楼，教育和司法部的办事处，造成4人死亡，25人受伤。巴勒斯坦报告还提到导弹落在了一个讲习班和一些货币兑换商的办公室里，其中一枚是接近儿童医院，略有破坏它。在拉法，空袭摧毁了5个走私通道和警察指挥中心，而在加沙城，据称武器的制造中心和储存设施被摧毁。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7806844.stm Gaza violence goes into sixth day] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7806844.stm |date=20090104082132 }} [[BBC_News|BBC News]]. 2009-01-01.</ref>数十名以色列人上午收到哈马斯短信警告说，对加沙地带的进攻只会带来巨大的火箭弹袭击。<ref name=Waked>{{cite web|title=Hamas sends text messages to Israeli cell phones|author=Ali Waked|date=2009-01-01|accessdate=2009-01-01|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3648799,00.html|archive-date=2009-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090118002613/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3648799,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>据以色列军方的消息，哈马斯发射超过50枚火箭弹，但没有造成人员伤亡。<ref name=AFP>{{cite web|title=Israeli raid kills Hamas leader on 6th day of blitz|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20090101/ts_afp/mideastconflictgaza|publisher=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|date=2009-01-01|accessdate=2009-01-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090101200415/http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20090101/ts_afp/mideastconflictgaza|archivedate=2009-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>
