一架以色列空军飞机向哈马斯高级领导人Nizar Rayan的住所投下了一吨重的炸弹，Nizar Rayan及他的孩子与太太等共10余名家属，当场死亡，<ref name=Harel>{{cite web|title=IDF targets senior Hamas figures|author=Haaretz Correspondents and Agencies, Amos Harel and Yoav Stern|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052052.html|date=2009-01-02|accessdate=2009-01-02|archive-date=2009-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122141258/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052052.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 还有30人受伤。<ref name=AP>{{cite web|title=Child casualties mount in besieged Gaza|author=The Associated Press|publisher=[[International_Herald_Tribune|International Herald Tribune]]|date=2009-01-01|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2009/01/01/news/ML-Gaza-Children-Casualties.php|accessdate=2009-01-01|archive-date=2009-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213154506/http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2009/01/01/news/ML-Gaza-Children-Casualties.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>在以色列空军炸死哈马斯高层领袖后，哈马斯下令展开报复行动。哈马斯也声称，可能恢复对以色列的[[自杀攻击|自杀攻击]]行动。<ref>[http://estate.chinanews.com.cn/gj/zd/news/2009/01-03/1511938.shtml]{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

=== 1月2日 ===
哈马斯下令发动“愤怒日”活动，誓言为前一日遭以色列空袭死亡的高级领导人Nizar Rayan复仇。同天在加沙地带和约旦河西岸成千上万的抗议者走上街头抗议。以色列警方向耶路撒冷和邻近村庄调动了数千名警力，以保持事态平静。<ref>[http://uk.news.yahoo.com/18/20090102/twl-israeli-attack-kills-brothers-as-ham-3cd7efd.html Israeli attack kills brothers as Hamas stages 'Day of Wrath']{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, ''Yahoo'', 02-01-2008</ref> <ref>[http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2009-01-03/072114973716s.shtml {{Wayback|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2009-01-03/072114973716s.shtml |date=20190608085803 }} 愤怒日</ref>以军对20个哈马斯官员住所发动空袭，<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7809154.stm Hamas warns against ground attack] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7809154.stm |date=20090104082939 }} ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]''. 2009-01-02.</ref>在汗尤尼斯有5名平民死亡。<ref>[http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/02/israel.gaza/index.html Israel bombs as tanks wait on outskirts of Gaza] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/02/israel.gaza/index.html |date=20090121084148 }} ''[[CNN_News|CNN News]]''. 2009-01-02.</ref>以军开始轰炸边界附近的地面，企图将地雷清除，越来越多的猜测，一场地面进攻迫在眉睫。以色列短暂开放埃雷兹过境点，使约440名持有外国护照居民离开加沙地带。<ref>[http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2009/01/200912145020649135.html Gaza mourns as strikes continue] {{Wayback|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2009/01/200912145020649135.html |date=20090203032408 }} ''[[Al-Jazeera|Al-Jazeera]].'' 2009-01-02.</ref> 

一整天，32枚火箭弹袭击了以色列；3人轻伤，一些建筑物受到严重破坏。<ref name="ynetnews_jan2">{{cite news | title=One injured as rocket hits Ashkelon home | date=2009-01-02 | publisher=[[ynetnews|ynetnews]] | url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649292,00.html | accessdate=2009-01-03 | archive-date=2009-01-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109024908/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649292,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 在[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]，男子未满50岁，或没有持以色列身份证将无法在[[阿克萨清真寺|阿克萨清真寺]]祈祷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ochaopt.org/documents/ocha_opt_gaza_situation_report_2009_01_02_english.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5dYZRlFLB?url=http://www.ochaopt.org/documents/ocha_opt_gaza_situation_report_2009_01_02_english.pdf |archive-date=2009-01-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 1月3日 ===
周六清晨，以色列空袭加沙地带打死了一名哈马斯高级指挥官Abu Zakaria al-Jamal。<ref name=Jan3Ynetnews>{{cite web|title=Hamas commander killed in Gaza strike|date=2009-01-03|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649466,00.html|accessdate=2009-01-03|archive-date=2009-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090105203514/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649466,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>Abu Zakaria al-Jamal是加沙火箭队指挥官。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/03/israel.gaza/ |title=Israeli ground troops enter Gaza |accessdate=2009-01-07 |archive-date=2018-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004235936/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/03/israel.gaza/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在另一起空袭中，哈马斯指挥官Jamal Mamduch被杀死。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nrg.co.il/online/1/ART1/834/737.html?hp=0&loc=1&tmp=4098|title=חיה"א חיסל מפקד בגדודי עז א-דין אל-קסאם בעזה|first=Amir|last=Buchbut|publisher=nrgמעריב|language=he|accessdate=2009-01-03|archive-date=2011-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604230608/http://www.nrg.co.il/online/1/ART1/834/737.html?hp=0&loc=1&tmp=4098|dead-url=yes}}</ref>许多哈马斯领导人与家人一起在自己家中遇害。以色列空军对贝特拉西亚发动空袭。13名巴勒斯坦人死于以军空袭，其中包括了6名儿童，数十人受伤。<ref name="BBC 7809699">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7809699.stm | title = Israel steps up offensive on Gaza | publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | date = 2009-01-02 | accessdate = 2009-01-03 | location = London, UK | archive-date = 2009-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090104150607/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7809699.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>至少34枚火箭弹在白天落在以色列，炸毁了几座建筑物，并有一名女子受轻伤。一些哈马斯的火箭弹击中贝尔谢巴一家空的学校。<ref name=Jpost_jan3>{{cite web|title=Cafeteria hit in early morning volley|publisher=[[Jerusalem_Post|Jerusalem Post]]|date=2009-01-03|url=http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733150873&pagename=JPost/JPArticle/ShowFull|accessdate=2009-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129110301/http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733150873&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull|archive-date=2012-01-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

傍晚，以色列地面部队开始进入加沙地带，展开第一次地面行动。<ref name="ynet_ground_troops_started">{{cite news | url = http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649729,00.html | title = IDF enters Gaza; dozens of terrorists hurt | accessdate = 2009-01-03 | date = 2009-01-03 | first = Hanan | last = Greenberg | archive-date = 2009-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090106024038/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3649729,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>同天[[日本内阁总理大臣|日本内阁总理大臣]][[麻生太郎|麻生太郎]]说，日本将向在以色列空袭中遭受重大人员伤亡的加沙地带提供价值1000万美元的紧急人道援助。<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2009-01/03/content_10598534.htm 日本表示要向加沙地带提供1000万美元人道援助]</ref>

=== 1月4日 地面攻势 ===
以色列地面部队进入加沙北部的拜特拉希耶和拜特哈嫩。<ref name="aljazeera4jan">[http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2009/01/20091322357629723.html Israeli ground troops enter Gaza] {{Wayback|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2009/01/20091322357629723.html |date=20090122140217 }}, ''Al Jazeera English''. 2009-01-04</ref>据报道，以色列军队分割包围加沙地带，但没有进入人口稠密区。<ref>[http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052299.html IDF soldier killed, another seriously wounded in Gaza ground operation] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67ZFhI21o?url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052299.html |date=20120510235845 |dateformat=iso }}, ''Haaretz'', 2009-01-04</ref>以色列军方称有40个目标遭到攻击，包括武器库和火箭弹发射点。尽管最高法院的判决允许有限数量的记者到战争前线，但以军还是拒绝让记者进入前线地区。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/7810270.stm Israel troops clash with Hamas] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/7810270.stm |date=20090106040109 }}BBC News</ref>激烈激战发生在[[加沙|加沙]]城附近，以色列国防军报告说，有30名士兵受伤。以色列政府还声称，至少50名哈马斯武装分子在夜间的地面行动被打死，还有几十人受伤。<ref>[http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3650149,00.html IDF deep in Strip: 50 terrorists killed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3650149,00.html |date=20090106052753 }} ''Ynetnews''. [2009-01-04]</ref>在周日晚些时候，在早先的迫击炮弹事件中，一名以色列士兵被打死。<ref name="haaretz_2nd_israeli_soldier_casualty">{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052299.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-08 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67ZFhI21o?url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052299.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733158821&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull |title=IDF soldier dies of wounds sustained in Gaza mortar fire |access-date=2011-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111175345/http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733158821&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull |archive-date=2012-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>巴勒斯坦医院人士称，至少21名巴勒斯坦人在战斗中被打死。<ref>[http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/04/israel.gaza/index.html Israeli forces push deeper into Gaza; death toll rises] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/04/israel.gaza/index.html |date=20091208042612 }} ''[[CNN_News|CNN News]]''. 2009-01-04.</ref>巴勒斯坦卫生部官员称，以色列炮弹落在一所学校附近的市场，造成至少17人死亡，130人受伤。一辆以军坦克在加沙北部开火造成12人死亡，其中显然包括平民。一枚以军导弹击中一所位于Shuja'iyya的房屋附近，造成一名母亲和她的四个孩子死亡。同天上午，一辆救护车在拜特拉希耶遭到炮击，4名医务人员受重伤。<ref name="ocha_report_1_4">{{Cite news
 |title       = Situation Report from the Humanitarian Coordinator - 4 January 2009 as of 17:00
 |url         = http://www.ochaopt.org/gazacrisis/admin/output/files/ocha_opt_gaza_situation_report_2009_01_04_english.pdf
 |date        = 2009-01-04
 |publisher   = [[UN|UN]] [[Office_for_the_Coordination_of_Humanitarian_Affairs|Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs]]
 |accessdate  = 2009-01-04
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/5daA4mm1G?url=http://www.ochaopt.org/gazacrisis/admin/output/files/ocha_opt_gaza_situation_report_2009_01_04_english.pdf
 |archivedate = 2009-01-04
 |dead-url    = yes
}}</ref>与此同时，至少有41个火箭弹和迫击炮弹从加沙地带飞入以色列境内的边界社区。<ref>[http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733159842&pagename=JPost/JPArticle/ShowFull 6 hurt as 45 rockets, shells hit South]{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, ''The Jerusalem Post''</ref>3名以色列平民受轻伤。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7810270.stm Israeli troops clash with Hamas] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7810270.stm |date=20120204012527 }} ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]''. 2009-01-04.</ref>

3名哈马斯高级领导人在周日被打死：Hussam Hamdan是负责哈马斯向以色列城市贝尔谢巴和Ofakim发射火箭弹的指挥官；Muhammad Hilo是负责向以色列发射远程火箭弹；Mohamad Shalpokh负责火箭弹发射。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733158821&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull |title=IAF kills 2 senior Hamas terrorists |access-date=2011-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111175345/http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733158821&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull |archive-date=2012-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ynet_2senior_hamas">{{cite news |title=Rockets fired at Ashdod, Ashkelon; top Hamas man killed |publisher=[[YNET|YNET]] |date=2009-01-04 |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3650161,00.html |accessdate=2009-01-04 |language=en |archive-date=2009-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106041031/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3650161,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/04/israel.gaza/index.html {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/meast/01/04/israel.gaza/index.html |date=20091208042612 }} Hamas sources say three leaders killed in Gaza[''CNN News''</ref><ref>[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/middle_east/article5446175.ece?token=null&offset=12&page=2 Israeli troops reach the edge of Gaza City] ''The Times''</ref>以色列安全局向内阁说哈马斯在国内和流亡的领导人认为，他们的组织正面临一个“现实的威胁”，并“愿意达成一项协议”的停火。不过，外交部长[[齐皮·利夫尼|齐皮·利夫尼]]说，以色列不打算与哈马斯谈判，因为这样会把哈马斯合法化作为一个谈判伙伴。

哈马斯称，[[阿克萨烈士旅|阿克萨烈士旅]]、人民抵抗委员会、[[杰哈德|杰哈德]]和[[解放巴勒斯坦人民阵线|解放巴勒斯坦人民阵线]]参加了反对以色列国防军的战斗。他们使用在2007年加沙之战中[[法塔赫|法塔赫]]遗留下来的武器。<ref>[http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733174237&pagename=JPost/JPArticle/ShowFull Hamas: We're using PA arms to battle IDF] {{Wayback|url=http://fr.jpost.com/servlet/Satellite?cid=1230733174237&pagename=JPost%2FJPArticle%2FShowFull |date=20120224113253 }}, ''The Jerusalem Post''</ref>据医疗人士说，当天巴勒斯坦人的死亡人数总共为42人，其中大多数是平民。<ref name=reutersjan5>{{cite news|title=Israel presses on with Gaza attack|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/wtMostRead/idUSLS69391620090105|date=2009-01-05|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2009-01-08|archive-date=2009-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108095058/http://www.reuters.com/article/wtMostRead/idUSLS69391620090105|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 1月5日 ===
[[File:Gaza-Israel_war_casualties_20090112.png|250px]]
以军控制了大部分加沙地带地区。由于越来越密集的激战，成千上万的加沙人逃离家园。以军和哈马斯在加沙的街头上展开激战，同时以军已经包围了加沙。<ref>{{cite news|last=McCarthy|first=Rory|title=Thousands flee guns and shells as Israel tightens grip on Gaza|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/05/israel-palestine-gaza-attacks|date=2009-01-05|accessdate=2009-01-08|archive-date=2013-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208070236/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/05/israel-palestine-gaza-attacks|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=reutersjan5/><ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/05/israel-palestine-gaza-attacks1 Israeli troops and Hamas fighters clash in Gaza City] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/05/israel-palestine-gaza-attacks1 |date=20130102194747 }} ''Guardian.co.uk''. 2009-01-05.</ref>一辆属于哈马斯卫生部的救护车在空袭中被击中，3名医务人员被炸死。<ref>http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5ioi_0jtO9RjMwPNRoXNCndRPRq3gD95GNHK80</ref>以军坦克的炮击，在加沙地带造成至少24名平民死亡，<ref>{{cite news|title=Israeli tank shelling kills at least 24,Palestinians|url=http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90852/6567488.html|date=2009-01-05|accessdate=2009-01-08|archive-date=2009-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090121183545/http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90852/6567488.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中在加沙Zaytun地区，一户住家的7名成员被打死，在另一起攻击中，一名怀孕的巴勒斯坦妇女和她的4个孩子被炸死。<ref name="Harel2">Harel, Amos. [http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1053120.html Three IDF soldiers killed, one critically wounded in Gaza blast] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1053120.html |date=20090811014926 }} ''[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]''. 2009-01-05.</ref>

包含昨日的這兩日，以色列對平民投擲各種殺傷力極強的化學炸彈，已被證實的有[[白磷彈|白磷彈]]和高密度不活性金屬炸藥（[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dense_Inert_Metal_Explosive Dense Inert Metal Explosive]{{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dense_Inert_Metal_Explosive |date=20201112032053 }}）。兩種化學炸彈的使用導致遺體均呈現全身嚴重碳化、下肢截斷且全身組織殘缺不全；倖存者均嚴重受傷致終身殘廢，且承受化學毒害帶來的永久痛苦。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/51506 |title=帝國恐怖主義 斷送巴勒斯坦和平 {{!}} 苦勞網<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2014-07-26 |archive-date=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730044642/http://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/51506 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://artintifada.wordpress.com/2009/01/16/israel-admits-using-phosphorus-bombs-on-gaza/ |title=Israel admits using phosphorus bombs on gaza {{!}} Artintifada<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archive-date=2019-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105004544/https://artintifada.wordpress.com/2009/01/16/israel-admits-using-phosphorus-bombs-on-gaza/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/systems/munitions/dime.htm |title=Dense Inert Metal Explosive (DIME)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2014-07-26 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126141053/https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/systems/munitions/dime.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://72.52.208.92/~gbpprorg/judicial-inc//Dense_Inert_Metal_Explosive.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808161922/http://72.52.208.92/~gbpprorg/judicial-inc//Dense_Inert_Metal_Explosive.htm |archive-date=2014-08-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

當時，諸多國際媒體報導以色列在军事行动中使用有争议的白磷弹。<ref name="DailyMail_WP">{{cite news| title=Gaza death toll soars past 500 as Israel is accused of using banned phosphorus shells| author=Matthew Kalman| date=2009-01-05| publisher=Daily Mail| url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1105127/Gaza-death-toll-soars-past-500-Israel-accused-using-banned-phosphorus-shells.html| accessdate=2009-01-09| archive-date=2019-08-22| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822000936/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1105127/At-14-children-killed-Gaza-terror-Israel-defies-demands-ceasefire.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://udn.com/NEWS/WORLD/WORS3/4673998.shtml | title=猛轟哈瑪斯_以疑用白磷彈 | date=2009-01-06 | accessdate=2009-01-11 | language=zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{cite news
