 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>但以色列表示他们使用白磷弹是用于制造烟雾掩护部队。没有任何条约禁止将白磷用于烟幕弹或照明弹。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://mil.huanqiu.com/Exclusive/2009-01/338803.html | title=英媒质疑以军使用白磷弹 或造成严重平民伤亡 | publisher=国新办网 | date=2009-01-08 | accessdate=2009-01-11 | language=zh-hans | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090114161909/http://mil.huanqiu.com/Exclusive/2009-01/338803.html | archive-date=2009-01-14 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>以色列在2006年在黎巴嫩使用白磷弹，英国和美国使用白磷弹在其他地方。以色列一直否认使用白磷弹。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sify.com/news/fullstory.php?id=14830411 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822000941/https://www.sify.com/sify_redirect.htm |archive-date=2019-08-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2010年2月1日, 以色列終承認曾經使用白磷彈, 並已懲罰兩名下令使用白磷彈攻擊的軍官。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2010/02/100201_israelgazainvestigation.shtml 以色列懲罰發射白磷彈軍官] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2010/02/100201_israelgazainvestigation.shtml |date=20140908132955 }}，BBC中文網。</ref>而高密度不活性金屬炸藥，以色列至今仍矢口否認曾經使用，相關消息僅在少數部落格內的文章被揭露。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://artintifada.wordpress.com/2009/01/18/israel-dime-weapon-effect-on-gaza-article-and-gallery/ |title=Israel DIME Weapon effect on Gaza-Article and Gallery {{!}} Artintifada<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630054834/https://artintifada.wordpress.com/2009/01/18/israel-dime-weapon-effect-on-gaza-article-and-gallery/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

哈马斯表示，将派遣一个代表团前往埃及，法国继续进行外交努力，希望能达成48小时的停火协议。以色列国防军仍然拒绝让记者进入加沙地带，尽管以色列最高法院准许接纳少量的记者。<ref name=bbcjan5>{{cite news|title=Envoys race to halt Gaza carnage|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7810945.stm|date=2009-01-05|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2009-01-09|archive-date=2009-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106194032/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7810945.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大规模的战斗从下午6时30左右开始，交战区域在加沙城东部。哈马斯使用迫击炮向以色列国防军发动袭击。在交火中，有两名以军士兵受伤，其中一人伤势严重。超过40枚火箭弹袭击了亚实基伦、[[阿什杜德|阿什杜德]]、斯代罗特、内蒂沃特、贝尔谢巴等以色列南部城镇。在阿什杜德火箭几乎摧毁了一间[[幼儿园|幼儿园]]。哈马斯最初声称曾杀害5名以色列士兵，但后来又增加了9名。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Hamas says 9 Israeli soldiers killed |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/world/view/20090104-181325/Hamas-says-9-Israeli-soldiers-killed |access-date=2009-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522115540/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/world/view/20090104-181325/Hamas-says-9-Israeli-soldiers-killed |archive-date=2011-05-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>哈马斯也宣称已抓获两名以色列士兵。以色列则否认这些说法，指责哈马斯搞“心理战”。<ref name="Haaretz2">{{cite news|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052544.html|title=Report: Hamas holding 2 Israeli soldiers; IDF: No knowledge of report|accessdate=2009-01-09|archive-date=2009-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106044150/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1052544.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在晚上，以色列国防军称，在当天地面战中他们打死了80到100名的哈马斯武装人员。尽管如此，哈马斯发射的火箭弹和迫击炮弹还是造成4名以色列人受伤。<ref>[http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651124,00.html Hamas adamant to strike back at IDF] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651124,00.html |date=20090106160355 }}, ''Ynetnews''.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.debka.com/ |title=Debka file |accessdate=2009-01-09 |archive-date=2014-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205111330/http://www.debka.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

以色列国防军发言人证实， 3名以色列士兵死于友军坦克误射，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651164,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-06 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211035554/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651164,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 可能是友军误把以色列士兵识别为恐怖分子。<ref name="ynewnews_6th_soldier_confirmation">{{cite news|title=Tank and infantry operations in Gaza investigated|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651434,00.html|date=2009-01-06|accessdate=2009-01-09|archive-date=2011-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110523021917/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651434,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>http://www.hdzxw.com/news/2009/1-7/FD_U_Article-1-59-24-295347.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.hdzxw.com/news/2009/1-7/FD_U_Article-1-59-24-295347.html |date=20181002183703 }} 以军“乌龙炮”自毙三士兵</ref> 约20名士兵受伤，包括上校旅长阿维佩莱德。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651165,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-09 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012123213/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3651165,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>还有一位以色列国防军军官也死于友军误射。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dover.idf.il/IDF/English/News/the_Front/09/01/0602.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124001227/http://dover.idf.il/IDF/English/News/the_Front/09/01/0602.htm |archive-date=2009-01-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

联合国官员说，以军还空袭了一座联合国学校，打死了三名巴勒斯坦人。该学校是一个数百名流离失所的巴勒斯坦人的临时难民营。<ref name=APIHT0601>{{cite web|title=3 men killed in Israeli airstrike at UN school|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2009/01/06/news/ML-Gaza-UN-School.php|author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=[[International_Herald_Tribune|International Herald Tribune]]|accessdate=2008-01-06|date=2009-01-06|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822000936/https://www.nytimes.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

