联合国的高级官员说，在加沙地带100万巴勒斯坦人中的70万人已经缺电缺水。<ref name=Burai>{{cite web|title=Israel strikes deeper into Gaza|author=Ahmed Burai and Jeffrey Fleishman|date=2009-01-06|accessdate=2009-01-06|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-gaza7-2009jan07,0,6192771.story|archive-date=2009-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090118111807/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-gaza7-2009jan07,0,6192771.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>

